      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INGA AMY (4) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at Ballarat following on from a second place finish (22.73) at this track the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including 10 wins. Can make amends. STEP ON AIR (8) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (22.75) at this track behind Fred's Fury in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to feature. ARGYLE EMMA (5) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (22.77) last time in a Grade 5 at Ballarat. Worth following up. ASTON EXCESS (7) can measure up with the right run.",
